# Django JWT Authentication API

This project is a Django REST Framework based backend application implementing JWT authentication.  
It provides user registration, login, profile management, and an authenticated user listing API.  
All APIs are tested using Postman.

---

## Features

- User Registration API
- JWT Authentication (Access & Refresh Token)
- Login using username and password
- Protected Profile APIs (GET, UPDATE, DELETE)
- Authenticated Get All Users API
- Role-free authentication (no superuser required)
- Secure password hashing (Django default)
- Tested using Postman

---

## Tech Stack

- Python
- Django
- Django REST Framework
- Simple JWT
- SQLite (default database)
- Postman (API testing)

